Endpoints Overview
No.Endpoint
B.1./placelimitorder
Description
Places a LIMIT type order.
NOTE: Must ensure it’s within approx 5% of LTP else it may
not get matched!
B.2.
/cancelorder
Cancels an existing order.
Endpoint 1 - /placelimitorder
URL - https://trade.nestex.one/api/v2/placelimitorder
This will create a LIMIT order. The parameters are identical to those used in the frontend
Note: Calling this API multiple times can result in MULTIPLE ORDERS! Please use the A.2
Orders list API to check if you’re unsure of the order status at any time. Do NOT repeat hits
blindly, and validate all input values to ensure there are no GIGO situations.
Input format
{
{
"apikey": "-- api key --",
"apisecret": "-- api secret --",
"cur": "LTC",
"side": "BUY",
"qty": "0.01",
"price": "50"
}
Output format
"order_id": 102274836,
"ttl": 8,
"success": "ok"
}Endpoint 2 - /cancelorder
URL - https://trade.nestex.one/api/v2/cancelorder
Note: Calling this API multiple times does not cause any side effects; but it is best to avoid
repeating requests unless you had a network error or suchlike.
Input format
{
{
"apikey": "-- api key --",
"apisecret": "-- api secret --",
"order_id": "102274836"
}
Output format
"ttl": 2,
"success": "ok"
}